<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.4.4">
<l>kañcaṉ puṇarppiṉil vanta kaṭiya cakaṭa mutaittu</l>
<l>vañcakap pēymakaḷ tuñca vāymulai vaitta pirāṉē</l>
<l>mañcaḷuñ ceṅkaḻu nīriṉ vācikai yumnāṟu cāntu</l>
<l>mañcaṉa muṅkoṇṭu vaittē ṉaḻakaṉē nīrāṭa vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Lord, who, having kicked the cruel cart</l>
<l rend="indent">that came as a contrivance of Kamsa,</l>
<l>placed [your] mouth on the breast</l>
<l rend="indent">of the deceiful demon woman so that she died,</l>
<l>I have brought turmeric, a garland of red lilies,</l>
<l rend="indent">fragrant sandal paste and kohl.</l>
<l>[My] beauty, come to bathe in water.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
